headline: FirstEnergy Foundation Supersizes United Way of Berks County "Big Cheese" Event with $100,000 Grant
summary: A $100,000 grant from The FirstEnergy Foundation to the United Way of Berks County's annual Big Cheese event is helping nourish children and adults facing food insecurity.
